Import-CheckITData

SYNOPSIS

Imports Excel data and routes it to the appropriate CheckIT global store (NodeList, Reports, TaskLog, ErrorLog, Templates, Preferences, CredStore).

SYNTAX

Import-CheckITData [-Path] [[-Worksheet]

DESCRIPTION

Uses Import-FromExcel to read an .xlsx file, inspects the columns and/or sheet names, and determines the best target store. If ambiguous, prompts the user to select the destination. Handles PSCustomObject/hashtable normalization for CLI/GUI.

EXAMPLES

EXAMPLE 1

Import-CheckITData -Path ‚ÄúC:\Transcripts\NodeList.xlsx‚Äù
